Subsection 1: Public Access \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 All plenary sessions of the Convention shall be open to the public and broadcast via the Public Square.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 2: Public Input \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Convention shall establish mechanisms for receiving and considering input from the public, including through the Public Square.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf2 \cb1 Section F: Duration and Conclusion\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 1: Time Limit \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Convention shall conclude its business within six (6) months of its commencement, unless extended by a two-thirds vote of the delegates.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 2: Final Report \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Upon conclusion, the Convention shall submit a final report to the World Congress and all National Legislatures, detailing its proposed amendments and the rationale for each.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf2 \cb1 Section G: Post-Convention Process\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 1: Transmittal of Proposals \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The World Congress shall, within thirty (30) days of receiving the Convention's final report, transmit the proposed amendments to the National Legislatures for ratification.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 2: Ratification Process \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The ratification process shall proceed as outlined in Chapter VII, Article 1, Section B of this Constitution.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

