Subsection 3: Revision History \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The full revision history of all documents shall be preserved and made publicly available, allowing for transparent tracking of changes over time.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

