\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The source code for all digital platforms utilized in the governance of the Federation, including but not limited to the Public Square, DigitalMe ID system, and voting mechanisms, shall be open source and publicly accessible.\
