\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Notwithstanding Subsection 1, specific security implementations may be exempted from full disclosure if deemed necessary by the World Congress, provided that such exemptions are regularly reviewed and minimized to the greatest extent possible.\
