Subsection 2: Air Quality Standards\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Federation shall establish and enforce stringent air quality standards that: \
