\ls124\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(c)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Are regularly updated based on the latest scientific evidence.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

