\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 2: Water Quality Standards\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Federation shall establish and enforce water quality standards that: \
\pard\tx20\tx425\pardeftab720\li425\fi-426\sa360\partightenfactor0
\ls125\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(a)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Ensure the safety of drinking water sources;\
\ls125\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(b)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Protect aquatic ecosystems;\
\ls125\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(c)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Prevent water pollution from industrial, agricultural, and domestic sources.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 3: Water Resource Management\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Federation shall implement sustainable water resource management practices to ensure long-term availability of clean water for all.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

