Subsection 1: Right to Ecological Integrity\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Every Person has the right to live in an environment with healthy, functioning ecosystems and rich biodiversity.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

