Subsection 1: Non-Discrimination\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The rights enumerated in this Article shall be enjoyed without discrimination, with special attention given to vulnerable and marginalized populations.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 2: Equitable Distribution\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Environmental benefits and burdens shall be distributed equitably among all segments of society.\
