Subsection 1: Access to Justice\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Every Person shall have access to effective legal and administrative processes to enforce the rights enumerated in this Article.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 \cb1 \kerning1\expnd1\expndtw5
Subsection 2: Remediation and Compensation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 In cases of environmental harm, affected individuals and communities shall have the right to prompt and adequate remediation and compensation.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

