\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The exercise of the rights set forth in Subsection 1 may be subject to such restrictions as are prescribed by Law and are necessary in a democratic society, in the interests of national security, public order, or public health and morals.\
