Subsection 2: Right to Association \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Every Person shall have the Right to freedom of association with others.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

