\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The rights enumerated in this Article may be subject only to such limitations as are prescribed by Law and are necessary in a democratic society in the interests of national security, public safety, public order, public health, or morals, or for the protection of the rights and freedoms of others.\
