\ls135\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(a)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Be sufficient to ensure a standard of living commensurate with human dignity for the employee and their dependents;\
\ls135\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(b)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Be supplemented, where necessary, by additional social protection measures as prescribed by Law.\
