\ls138\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(b)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Reasonable limitation of working hours, as prescribed by Law;\
\ls138\ilvl0\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(c)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Periodic holidays with remuneration, the frequency and duration of which shall be determined by statute.\
