Subsection 2: Employer Obligations \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Employers shall be obligated to respect and facilitate the exercise of these rights, subject to penalties as established by Law.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

