Subsection 3: Transparency \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 All entities collecting or processing personal data shall be required to provide clear, concise, and easily accessible information about the nature, purpose, and extent of data collection and usage.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

