Subsection 2: Breach Notification \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 In the event of a data breach, affected individuals must be notified promptly and comprehensively, as prescribed by Law.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

