\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 Every Person shall have the right to pursue legal action against individuals or entities responsible for the generation, distribution, or hosting of content described in Subsection 1.\
