Subsection 5: Education and Prevention \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Federation shall establish programs to educate the public about the risks and consequences of digital misrepresentation and exploitation.\
