Subsection 6: International Cooperation \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The Federation shall pursue international agreements to facilitate the global enforcement of the rights established in this Section.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

