\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The World Congress may, by Law, provide for limited exceptions to the requirements of this Section for purposes of national security, criminal investigations, or other compelling public interests, subject to strict oversight and judicial review.\
