\pard\pardeftab720\sa360\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs26 \cf3 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 The World Congress shall, by Law, establish penalties for entities that fail to comply with the data traceability and association requirements, commensurate with the nature and severity of the non-compliance.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl288\slmult1\sa40\partightenfactor0

