\ls152\ilvl1\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(i)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Securing due recognition and respect for the Rights and Freedoms of others; and\
\ls152\ilvl1\cf3 \cb1 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone {\listtext	(ii)	}\cf3 \cb4 \up0 \nosupersub \ulnone Meeting the just requirements of morality, public order, and the general Wellness and Welfare in a Democratic Society.\
